summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a deed to Lots 11, 12 and 13, Block M, Carleton Beach Tracts and portion of the southeast one-quarter of Section 36, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M. for street purposes and laying off Perkins Lane West and an alley in the block bounded by Palatine Avenue North, Greenwood Avenue North, North 90th Street and North 92nd Street.
